WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: uz

00:00:00.370 --> 00:00:03.910
Siz media ijro ettiruvchi ilova bilan 
foydali bo‘lgan tajribani orttirasiz, lekin

00:00:03.910 --> 00:00:06.190
siz shunchaki kerakli kod satrlaridan
nusxa olib, undan foydalanishingiz mumkin.

00:00:06.190 --> 00:00:09.270
Ehtimol sizda bularning barchasi 
aynan qanday ishlashi haqida 

00:00:09.270 --> 00:00:10.280
savollar bordir.

00:00:10.280 --> 00:00:12.250
Keling, endi aynan shu haqida gaplashaylik.

00:00:12.250 --> 00:00:16.590
Shunday qilib, media ijro etuvchi ya’ni, "media player" 
murakkab sinfdir, chunki u ham audio, ham video fayllarni 

00:00:16.590 --> 00:00:17.870
ijro ettirishi mumkin.

00:00:17.870 --> 00:00:20.360
Ushbu media fayllarni 
ilova bilan birlashtirish mumkin,

00:00:20.360 --> 00:00:24.230
xuddi qo‘shiqni bizning oldingi oddiy ilovamizga 
kiritilgani kabi, yoki qo‘shiqlarni internetdan 

00:00:24.230 --> 00:00:26.160
to‘g‘ridan-to‘g‘ri uzatish mumkin.

00:00:26.160 --> 00:00:29.260
Media ijro ettiruvchining imkoniyatlari 
haqida batafsil tushuncha berish uchun,

00:00:29.260 --> 00:00:32.180
bu yerda "Android" dagi media ijro 
etuvchini qo‘llab-quvvatlaydigan 

00:00:32.180 --> 00:00:33.510
turli xil fayllarning barcha ro‘yxati berilgan.

00:00:33.510 --> 00:00:39.780
Shunday qilib, biz bu yerda "MP3" , "AAC" ,
"WAV" va boshqa juda ko‘p fayllarga ega bo‘lamiz.

00:00:39.780 --> 00:00:43.430
Aytgancha, fayl turlari - bu audio hajmini 
minimallashtirish va ovoz sifatini saqlab qolish 

00:00:43.430 --> 00:00:47.650
bilan birga, audio formatni raqamli formatda 
saqlashni amalga oshirishga turli xil yondoshishlardir.

00:00:47.650 --> 00:00:53.646
Bu xuddi tasvir turlarining 
"JPEG" , "GIF" , "PNG" va boshqalar

00:00:53.646 --> 00:00:55.232
kabi bo‘lishiga o‘xshaydi.

00:00:55.232 --> 00:00:58.797
Demak, biz sizga "MYEQ" 
ilovasida Andrea so‘zlarini baland ovozda 

00:00:58.797 --> 00:01:01.250
talaffuz qiladigan "MP3" fayllarini taqdim etamiz.

00:01:01.250 --> 00:01:03.590
Shu tarzda siz audio fayllarni ilova 
ichiga kiritishingiz mumkin,

00:01:03.590 --> 00:01:05.040
bunda endi siz fayllarni
internetdan uzatishingiz shart emas.

